{"title":"雨夜歌声","authors":["张兰生"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨夜歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军战士　张兰生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部队夜行军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路宿小松林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雨哗哗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电又雷鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士都惊醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身湿淋淋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听笛子响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨夜传歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺着笛声望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨中一人影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个子高又大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声真动人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是连长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家围着他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声绕山岭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨夜开晚会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这事真新颖；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱起家乡调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分外动人听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛子伴歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢笑迎黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮大红日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升上高山顶……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}